name: FNF VS STEVE THE BUNNY
description:
This is a fnf mod with Steve The Bunny. It has 4 songs (Doge Tutorial, Hi there, Annoyed and Exploding). At the end you can shoot with a gun . This fnf mod is made in Scratch. There are also memes in it.

No bunnies were harmed in the making of this fnf mod.

Huge credit to ninjamuffin99.
